sentences.sentence: Over 200 executions were carried out last year.
General Sachet is ordered to oversee such executions.
sentences.translation: 萨西尔将军受命监督了这些处决。

sentences.sentence: She said to herself, for she had felt quite unhappy at the number of executions the Queen had ordered.
sentences.translation: 她自言自语地，因为她对王后下令处决的人数感到很不高兴。
